quran[12]{c,v,t,f}:
  19,79,"Rárá. A máa ṣàkọsílẹ̀ ohun tó ń wí. A sì máa fẹ ìyà lójú fún un tààrà."
  19,80,"A ó sì jogún ohun tó ń wí fún un. Ó sì máa wá bá Wa ní òun nìkan."
  19,81,"Wọ́n sọ àwọn kan di ọlọ́hun lẹ́yìn Allāhu nítorí kí wọ́n lè fún wọn ní agbára."
  20,61,"(Ànábì Mūsā) sọ fún wọn pé: “Ègbé yín ò! Ẹ má ṣe dá àdápa irọ́ mọ́ Allāhu nítorí kí Ó má baà fi ìyà pa yín rẹ́. Àti pé dájúdájú ẹnikẹ́ni tí ó bá dá àdápa irọ́ (mọ́ Allāhu) ti pòfo.”"
  20,62,"Wọ́n fọ̀rọ̀ jomi toro ọ̀rọ̀ láààrin ara wọn. Wọ́n sì tẹ̀ sọ̀rọ̀."
  20,63,"Wọ́n wí pé: “Dájúdájú àwọn méjèèjì yìí, òpìdán ni wọ́n o. Wọ́n fẹ́ mu yín jáde kúrò lórí ilẹ̀ yín pẹ̀lú idán wọn ni. Wọ́n sì (fẹ́) gba ojú ọ̀nà yín tó dára jùlọ mọ yín lọ́wọ́."
  21,37,"Wọ́n fi ìkánjú sínú àdámọ́ ènìyàn. Mo máa fi àwọn àmì Mi hàn yín. Nítorí náà, ẹ má ṣe kán Mi lójú."
  21,38,"Wọ́n ń wí pé: “Ìgbà wo ni àdéhùn yìí yóò ṣẹ tí ẹ bá jẹ́ olódodo?”"
  21,39,"Tí ó bá jẹ́ pé àwọn tó ṣàì gbàgbọ́ mọ ìgbà tí wọn kò níí dá Iná dúró níwájú wọn àti ní ẹ̀yìn wọn, tí A ò sì níí ràn wọ́n lọ́wọ́, (wọn ìbá tí wá ìyà pẹ̀lú ìkánjú)."
  22,13,"Ó ń pe ohun tí ìnira rẹ̀ súnmọ́ ju àǹfààní rẹ̀ lọ. Dájúdájú (òrìṣà) burú ní aláfẹ̀yìntì, ó sì burú ní alásùn-únmọ́."
  22,14,"Dájúdájú Allāhu yóò mú àwọn tó gbàgbọ́ ní òdodo, tí wọ́n sì ṣe àwọn iṣẹ́ rere wọ inú Ọgbà Ìdẹ̀ra tí àwọn odò ń ṣàn ní ìsàlẹ̀ rẹ̀. Dájúdájú Allāhu ń ṣe ohun tí Ó bá fẹ́."
  22,15,"Ẹnikẹ́ni tí ó bá lérò pé Allāhu kò níí ran (Ànábì - kí ìkẹ́ àti ọlà Allāhu máa bá a -) lọ́wọ́ láyé àti lọ́run, kí ó na okùn sí sánmọ̀ (àjà ilé rẹ̀) lẹ́yìn náà kí ó gé e (ìyẹn ni pé, kí ó pokùn so). Kí ó wò ó nígbà náà bóyá ète rẹ̀ lè mú (àrànṣe) tó ń bínú sí kúrò (lọ́dọ̀ Ànábì - kí ìkẹ́ àti ọlà Allāhu máa bá a -).{1}.",1:[Ìyẹn ni pé, abínú-ẹni kò lè pa kádàrá-ẹni dà. Ó kàn fẹ́ han ara rẹ̀ léémọ̀ ni.]
